                    <span>This book really opens your eyes to the world of hacking (how to stop it). I presume the auther is a hacker and his insight and detail make this book a must for sysadmin. I recommend the book to basically anyone running Linux (or Unix) even beginners, because of it's great explanations.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Understandable and Effective Advice</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
